	<h1 class="title">话剧《北京法源寺》的导演说，她的戏里都是宏大的东西 | 100 个有想法的人</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/117425/small/117425.?1433669313" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王珊珊 孙今泾</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-18 17:36:49 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20672/medium/20672.JPG?1452685363" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


